  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is meant to assess the safety and tolerability of idebenone in patients with
      Friedreich's Ataxia over a 12 months period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study involves 6 clinic visits.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
